### 7. Hardcoded Port / No Environment Configuration (OWASP A05: Security Misconfiguration)

Port `3000` is hardcoded. In production, configuration should come from environment variables to avoid port conflicts and enable proper deployment.

```js
const PORT = process.env.PORT || 3000;
app.listen(PORT, () => {
  console.log(`Server running on port ${PORT}`);
});
```

---

